[{"Id": 1014934, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Abu-Basir is reported to have said: I complained to Imam Sadiq (a) about poverty and asked him to teach me a supplicatory prayer for sustenance. He therefore taught me a supplicatory prayer after which I have never needed anything. Precisely, the Imam (a) instructed me to say the following supplicatory prayer in the Night Prayer while I am in the position of prostration…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Abu Baseer se manqool hai keh mai ne Imam Jafar Sadiq (a) se apni haajaat ka zikr kiya aur arz kiya keh mujhe wuz’at-e-rizq ki koi dua taaleem farmaaye, pas Aap (a) ne mujhe yeh dua taaleem farmaayi aur mai ne jab isko padhna shuru kiya kabhi mohtaaj nahi huwa. Aap (a) ne farmaaya keh Namaz-e-Shab mein sajdeh ki haalat mein kaho…", "UrduDescription": "ابو بصیر سے منقول ہے کہ میں نے امام جعفر صادق ؑ سے اپنی حاجات کا ذکر کیا اور عرض کیا : مجھے وسعتِ رزق کی کوئی دعا تعلیم فرمائیں تو آپ نے مجھے یہ دعا تعلیم فرمائی اور میں نے جب اس کو پڑھنا شروع کیا کبھی محتاج نہیں ہوا، آپؑ نے فرمایا : نمازِ تہجد میں سجدے کی حالت میں کہو۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGre